{"tid":2257134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣驅逐港人李彬豪出境　因非法跟蹤拍攝香港學運人士","createTime":"2020-10-25T02:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T04:08:06.000Z","uid":51271,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cad3503d06f0f0cba1b475678ee904febe8b30eb","tid":2257134,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:39:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>CONDOM呀，去大灣區啦柒頭</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556551-20201025.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556551-20201025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=9e041b23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556551-20201025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f2e824b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556551-20201025.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n在台北，移民署指香港人李彬豪在台灣不法從事跟蹤拍攝在台香港學運人士，違反港澳條例等規定，廢止他在台居留許可，今天強制驅逐出境，一定期間不得到台灣。<br />\n<br />\n李彬豪被指委託台灣的私家偵探，跟蹤拍攝香港學運人士鍾翰林在台活動，照片交予香港傳媒刊登。李彬豪則聲稱受香港一家私家偵探委託，到台灣再委託私家偵探跟蹤。<br />\n<br />\n內政部長徐國勇表示，不論本地民眾及外來人士，在台灣都有免於恐懼的自由，部分紅色傳媒以不法手段在台灣收集情報，明顯利用台灣的自由民主進行滲透、傷害人權，其行為不為民主法治社會認同。"},{"pid":"7911aa785a124c3687b52d5430b3c375e25626a8","tid":2257134,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:44:22.000Z","msg":"仆街共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ed6c7a93b43319fd4313ef8f1e536f2257c328","tid":2257134,"uid":364767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"全球民主國家都應趕走所有赤共陸撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e0e66d2cc688779d